{
  "id": "adv_event_2604_01_01",
  "title": "出掛けた先は",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ラジオの生放送終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.4666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……私としたことが\n生放送で告知を言い間違えるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3333333413,
      "endTime": 8.8666669289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんが間違えるなんてめずらしいね\n集中出来てなかったみたいだけど、何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8666669289,
      "endTime": 16.7285265367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.0604677088
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.9285263459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "実は気になることがあって……。最近、葵ちゃんが\n寮を抜け出して夜遊びしているみたいなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9285263459,
      "endTime": 24.333333587600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えーっ、そうなの！？\n夜中に出掛けてるなんて全然気付かなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3285267274,
      "endTime": 31.1946492593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.5666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.3946490686
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私も外出するところを偶然見かけて気付いたんです\nもし悪い遊びをしてるなら見過ごす訳にはいきません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3946490686,
      "endTime": 40.0107491892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.1946490686
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私の思い過ごしかもしれませんし……\nせめて、どこで何をしているか分かればいいんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1946490686,
      "endTime": 48.6224719446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなら芽衣に任せて！\n葵ちゃんが何をしてるか、芽衣が突き止めてあげる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.594652629,
      "endTime": 55.95750978,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9762.8569484
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8000041962
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.2506778166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――週末の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9575095893,
      "endTime": 58.1241734585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.1241734585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "電車が遅延したせいで、仕事から帰るのが遅くなったわ\nみんなはもう寝ちゃったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0241734585,
      "endTime": 66.361135014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.5611348233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "すやすや……\nえへへ～、もう食べられないよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5611348233,
      "endTime": 75.82981921049999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14572.198637200003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.8964846692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……玄関脇の茂みで寝ちゃってる子がいるわね\n芽衣、起きなさい。こんな所で寝たら風邪を引くわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8964846692,
      "endTime": 86.4454642377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.1333334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……あれ？\n怜ちゃん、おはよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3787938199,
      "endTime": 93.2075015149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.6585821658
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.4408234678
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "おはようじゃないでしょ\nどうしてこんな場所で寝てるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4408234678,
      "endTime": 97.8423235023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.0423233115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "見つからないように隠れて玄関を見張ってたんだけど\nついうとうとしちゃって……。あ、怜ちゃん隠れて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0423233115,
      "endTime": 107.6398746573,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11914.221866999995
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11257.676688499998
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17057.68206890001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.6628706932
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.7398729407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "何よ、いきなり……あら？　あれは……葵？\nこんな時間にどこへ行くのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7398729407,
      "endTime": 119.3957055511,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17526.2130337
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 109.8232090596
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.133335495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "それを今から確かめるんだよ！\nじゃあ、芽衣は尾行してくるね！　行ってきまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3957050407,
      "endTime": 126.7767258728,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9637.628419799996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.0269985832
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.9767256821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと芽衣！　待ちなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9767256821,
      "endTime": 130.3614875401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.6114873494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。事情は分かったわ\n確かに、葵が夜中に何をしているか気になるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6614873494,
      "endTime": 141.4950023259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.733335495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "どこかに向かってるみたいだけど、待ち合わせかな？\nそれとも、夜にやってるお店に行くとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.495005187,
      "endTime": 149.74822507759998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.6911321132
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.9482248869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "夜の店……そういえば、アイドルの先輩が言っていたわ\n夜、仕事帰りにサウナをキメるのがたまらないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9482248869,
      "endTime": 160.4095627394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
